  "body": "Hi\r\n\r\nWhen running tests and tasks, you can select the network with the `--network` parameter. \r\n\r\nBut how do you select the network when running a JS file directly!?\r\n\r\nWell, I discover it after a few hours of search, you can set this env variable `HARDHAT_NETWORK=rinkeby`.\r\n\r\nI suggest to add this in this section of the docs:\r\nhttps://hardhat.org/hardhat-network/#hardhat-network\r\n\r\nThanks!\r\n\r\n",
